---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="关于">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-12 reveal">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-medium">关于</h1>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-50 mt-1">About</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p>你好，我是李华，一个普通高中生。</p>
        <p>写这个博客是为了记录一些乱七八糟的想法和踩过的坑。</p>

        <h2>技术方向</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>前端</strong> — React, Vue, Next.js, Nuxt.js, Astro</li>
          <li><strong>移动端</strong> — Android, Flutter, React Native</li>
          <li><strong>后端</strong> — Python, Java, Kotlin, Go, Rust, Node.js</li>
          <li><strong>数据库</strong> — MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis</li>
          <li><strong>DevOps</strong> — Docker, Jenkins, Nginx, Cloudflare Workers</li>
          <li><strong>AI/ML</strong> — PyTorch, TensorFlow, OpenCV</li>
          <li><strong>设计</strong> — Figma, Blender, Adobe 全家桶</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>本站技术栈</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Astro — 静态站点生成器</li>
          <li>Tailwind CSS + daisyUI — 样式框架</li>
          <li>TypeScript — 类型安全</li>
          <li>MDX — 内容管理</li>
          <li>Cloudflare Workers — 部署</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>链接</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/real-LiHua">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://codeberg.org/lihua">Codeberg</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/lihua">GitLab</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://bangumi.tv/user/lihua">Bangumi</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://orcid.org/0009-0007-0253-0450">ORCID</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>联系</h2>
        <p>欢迎通过 Telegram 或者邮件与我交流。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script>
    import "../scripts/scroll-reveal";
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
